messages.msg: Welcome to our site! If you are looking for prayer or someone to chat with, reply to this message or email us at prayer@fightlust.com

I want to renounce every way of satan I want my heart soften to the things of God I want to renounce every way that I have hurt my wife I want to be cleansed from all sexual sins I want to renounce all evil demonic way

It sounds like you're seeking a powerful prayer for healing and renunciation. Here's a prayer you can use:

"Heavenly Father, I come before you today to renounce every way of Satan in my life. I ask that you soften my heart to the things of God. I renounce every way that I have hurt my wife and seek cleansing from all sexual sins. I also renounce all evil and demonic ways that have influenced my life. In the name of Jesus Christ, I ask for your forgiveness and healing. Thank you for your grace and mercy."

If you need further support or guidance, feel free to ask!
I ask God to turn me from a worldly husband into a Godly husband I repent for every way that I have hurt God my wife

It's wonderful that you're seeking transformation and repentance. You can pray something like this:

"Dear God, I ask you to turn me from a worldly husband into a Godly husband. I repent for every way that I have hurt you and my wife. Please cleanse my heart and guide me in your ways. Help me to love and serve my wife as you intend. Thank you for your forgiveness and for the opportunity to grow in my faith."

If you need more resources or support, just let me know!

I want to be free from all worldly desires I want to know God personally I ask God to draw me into a true relationship with him I want to serve him in spirit and truth I want deliverance from all falsehood hypocrisy double mindness and sexual impurity

It's great to hear your desire for freedom and a deeper relationship with God. You can pray this:

"Lord, I want to be free from all worldly desires. I ask you to draw me into a true relationship with you. Help me to serve you in spirit and truth. I seek deliverance from all falsehood, hypocrisy, double-mindedness, and sexual impurity. Please cleanse my heart and guide me in your ways. Thank you for your love and grace."

If you need further assistance or resources, feel free to reach out!
I want freedom from anger coveting and idolatry and lust

You can pray this for freedom:

"Heavenly Father, I come before you seeking freedom from anger, coveting, idolatry, and lust. I ask for your strength to overcome these struggles and to fill my heart with your peace and love. Help me to focus on you and to seek your will in my life. Thank you for your forgiveness and grace."

If you need more support or specific prayers, just let me know!
